description:
go.talks: more build-fixing
I still can't seem to get my head around the difference between
        cd code.google.com/p/go.talks
        go build ./...
and
        go build code.google.com/p/go.talks/...
They build different things. An exercise for the reader.
Anyway, this CL fixes problems found by the latter command.
Maybe it will make the go.talks builder go green.
